Copy this file to android/key.properties and fill in real values.
NEVER commit android/key.properties — it is gitignored.

Generate a keystore using:
keytool -genkey -v -keystore android/keystore/dukaan-ai-release.jks \
	-alias dukaan-ai -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000

storeFile=../keystore/dukaan-ai-release.jks
storePassword=YOUR_STORE_PASSWORD
keyAlias=dukaan-ai
keyPassword=YOUR_KEY_PASSWORD
